      "content": "This plan outlines a sophisticated AI-driven platform for scientific discovery, focusing on generating original research, planning study paths, and integrating cross-disciplinary knowledge. Due to the highly specialized and custom nature of the described AI engines and research planning systems, these functionalities cannot be fulfilled by standard Wix Apps or Wix CMS. Therefore, this plan focuses on the foundational structure for such a platform, acknowledging that the core AI and logic components would require custom development beyond the scope of typical Wix offerings."
